## Installation
```bash
  pip install ImageEnhancer
```
    
## Usage

```python
from ImageEnhancer import ImageUpscaler

# Initialise the upscaler
upscaler = ImageUpscaler()

# Launch the Gradio Interface
upscaler.launchInterface()
```


